No purchase necessary. Void where prohibited. GOTW 1 Giveaway starts December 2 at 11 a.m. and ends December 4 at 12 p.m. Must be 18+ and US resident to participate. To enter, follow @Walgreens, like this post and tag two friends in the comment section. Commenting on Post, replying to any entries made by other personal Instagram accounts or sharing the Post are not valid methods of Entry. Limit one (1) Entry per Instagram account holder. Any Entries received in excess of the entry limit or Entries that Sponsor finds inappropriate at Sponsor\xe2\x80\x99s discretion will be disqualified. Winner will be notified via DM on December 4. Sponsor reserves the right to modify or cancel this Giveaway at its discretion. Sponsored by Walgreen Co. Giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by Instagram."

b'Need some extra treats to make your Halloween sweet? We\xe2\x80\x99re here for all your candy needs. :jack-o-lantern: 
.
.
.
.
. 
:camera_with_flash: @thefreckledfox This year has brought a lot of changes for sure, but with\xc2\xa0@walgreens\xc2\xa0on our side, we\xe2\x80\x99re not gonna let anything interfere with our favorite holiday!\xc2\xa0#Ad\xc2\xa0

As you can see, we take Halloween prep V seriously around here! haha Every year when October hits, we sit down together and make a to-do list for the best Halloween season ever. Then, we head off to\xc2\xa0@walgreens\xc2\xa0to fill up on ALL the candy for the best prices around! We can always count on Walgreens to have everyone\xe2\x80\x99s favorite candy brands, not to mention we can pick up any other last-minute finishing touches we might be missing for our costumes, our spooky decor, all the fall activities we have planned, and of course what we need for our traditional epic Halloween party!

It\xe2\x80\x99s about the candy though, let\xe2\x80\x99s be real. It starts and ends with candy, and I\xe2\x80\x99m not mad about it. hahaha\xc2\xa0@Walgreens\xc2\xa0offers several fast and easy ways to get what you need to celebrate with locations minutes away and drive-thru or curbside pickup!\xc2\xa0

You can swipe up in my stories to find a\xc2\xa0@walgreens\xc2\xa0store near you! And now if you please, I\xe2\x80\x99d love to hear your favorite Halloween tradition in the comments below!

Xoxo'

b'This Juneteenth, we pledge to work toward an anti-racist society & affirm our support of the Black Lives Matter movement. Today, we share our commitment to racial equality by investing in two local Chicago organizations doing impactful work, as we continue to build a long-term action plan toward diversity, inclusion & safety for Black people.'

b'Our commitment to the communities we serve is absolute. Therefore, we promise to: 
Work quickly to reopen affected stores and partner with local organizations to help communities rebuild and heal. 
Find new ways to ensure access to healthcare in underserved black communities. 
Continue the work of our global diversity committee to drive accountability and assure that we are a truly diverse organization.'
